channel.title: Starting Over!
channel.description: Hey! I'm looking to start over on making a private server! I was thinking about maybe something oldschool like before 317+, but don't know where to start (Don't mention the search button...). I was wondering if something before 317 would be harder to code? If not, I'm basically looking for a clean to semi-clean source I could use to start working on it. If it is harder to code, what would be a good 317 alternative to start coding again? Looking for a clean to semi-clean, stable base on that one as well.
